  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Implementation of sexual health support program in oncology department. This program is
      organized in 3 axes. One is to inform the side effects of treatment on sexual health.

      There is a counselling team (nurse, esthetician,sexologue..etc) to raise the subject with
      patient and partner .

      Finally, the oncologist continue during the treatment to evaluate the benefit of this program
      and adapt their counselling according to the needs
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
